MesGUI, a library for creating simple interfaces, in OpenGL
Version 1.0

-- Author
Eric Maxey, em32@mail.csuchico.edu

-- How to install under Windows

Open msvc/mesGUI.dsw and navigate to Build->Batch Build
Click build
This will create a .lib file in the lib directory,
and an example program in the bin directory

-- How to install under Unix

make
make install
make test       <-- this will create bin/test_mesgui

-- What you need

OpenGL
FreeType2 (http://www.freetype.org)
SDL (http://www.libsdl.org)

